{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d0b6c22b08","title":"关于志愿军按预定计划入朝作战致邓华等电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"6132d54c77","index":0,"year":1950,"month":10,"day":18,"articleId":"d0b6c22b08"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji29","name":"毛泽东全集第29卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/29-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji29":{"comments":[{"id":"1962ce0cd3","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"d0b6c22b08","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"邓华，当时任中国人民志愿军第十三兵团司令员兼政治委员。2]洪、韩，指洪学智、韩先楚，当时均任中国人民志愿军第十三兵团副司令员。解，指解方，当时任中国人民志愿军第十三兵团参谋长。"},{"id":"e270c78118","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"d0b6c22b08","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指中国人民解放军东北军区副司令员贺晋年。"},{"id":"31503c4314","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"d0b6c22b08","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"安东，即今辽宁丹东市。"},{"id":"8a4b99fa23","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"d0b6c22b08","index":4,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"高岗，当时任中国人民解放军东北军区司令员兼政治委员。德怀，即彭德怀，当时任中国人民志愿军司令员兼政治委员。"}],"contents":[{"id":"0e2d064d0e","type":"title","text":"关于志愿军接预定计划人朝作战致邓华等电","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"d0b6c22b08"},{"id":"1962ce0cd3","type":"paragraph","text":"邓、洪、韩、解，并告贺副司令以：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"d0b6c22b08"},{"id":"e270c78118","type":"paragraph","text":"四个军及三个炮师决接预定计划进入朝北作战，自明（十九日晚）从安东和辑安线开始渡鸭绿江。为严格保守秘密，渡河部队每日黄昏开始至婴晨四时即停止，五时以前隐蔽完毕并须切实检查。为取得经验，第一晚（十九日晚）准备渡两个至三个师，第二晚再增加或减少，再行翻的情形，余由高岗、德怀面告","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"d0b6c22b08"},{"id":"31503c4314","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"d0b6c22b08"},{"id":"8a4b99fa23","type":"para